  <brief_title>A Trial of Restrictive Versus Traditional Blood Transfusion Practices in Burn Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Clinical Trial of Restrictive vs. Traditional Blood Transfusion Practices in Burn Patients</official_title>
